imm%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20agency%20in%202018%20as%20creative%20affairs%20executive%2C%20will%20expand%20her%20role%20to%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Alex%20Ritman%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fuk-agency-casarotto-sets-new-leadership-jodi-shields-1236449207%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Plus-size%20clothes%20are%20disappearing%20in%20the%20Ozempic%20era%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ozempic%20on%20a%20hanger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686577d23d5881a51c1c910f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Rebecca%20Zisser%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETess%20Holliday%20remembers%202019%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bglorious%26quot%3B%20year%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-body-positive-moments-2019%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplus-size%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20body%20positivity.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftess-holliday-wears-strawberry-dress-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplus-size%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20body%20activist%20walked%20the%20runway%20at%20New%20York%20Fashion%20Week.%20She'd%20been%20featured%20by%20magazines%20such%20as%20Cosmopolitan%20UK%2C%20Nylon%2C%20and%20Self.%20The%20cultural%20shift%20felt%20palpable%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frihanna-savage-x-fenty-show-versus-victorias-secret-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERihanna's%20Savage%20X%20Fenty%20runway%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20headlines%20for%20the%20size%20diversity%20of%20its%20models%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Flizzo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELizzo%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20topping%20the%20charts%20with%20catchy%20songs%20and%20a%20message%20of%20empowerment.%20%26quot%3BIt%20finally%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20in%20a%20place%20where%20that%20was%20the%20norm%2C%26quot%3B%20Holliday%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20optimistic%20new%20norm%2C%20however%2C%20was%20short-lived.%20The%20pandemic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20all%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fok-to-turn-off-camera-video-calls-causing-zoom-dysmorphia-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZoom%20calls%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20had%20people%20picking%20their%20appearance%20apart.%20Some%20major%20brands%20that%20had%20made%20forays%20into%20the%20plus-size%20realm%20scaled%20back.%20Then%20came%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOzempic%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffda-compounded-tirzepatide-semaglutide-shortage-ozempic-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20weight-loss%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20promising%20miracles%20that%20could%20move%20shoppers%20out%20of%20the%20plus-size%20section%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20really%20see%20it%20getting%20better%20or%20shifting%20to%20a%20place%20where%20we%20are%20maybe%20hearing%20the%20term%20body%20positivity%20and%20seeing%20brands%20promote%20it%20in%20the%20way%20that%20they%20were%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Holliday%2C%20the%20author%20of%20the%20coming%20book%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D15b2f38c242376ba00121b139326b846477de157aa10bbc6197d95431ade83c5%26postID%3D6862da303d1ce42a6af4153b%26postSlug%3Dplus-size-clothing-ozempic-glp-1-weight-loss-drugs-shopping-2025-7%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FTake-Up-Space-Yall-Self-Love%252Fdp%252F0762489154%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETake%20Up%20Space%2C%20Y'all%3A%20Your%20Bold%20%26amp%3B%20Bright%20Guide%20to%20Self-Love%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20look%20at%20what%20happened%20with%20the%20backswing%20of%20diversity%20and%20inclusivity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-obsessed-exercise-shortcuts-lose-weight-easily-fitness-workout-hacks-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThin%20is%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20culturally%2C%20and%20the%20fashion%20industry%20is%20happy%20to%20oblige.%20Manufacturing%20plus-size%20clothes%20presents%20unique%20operational%20challenges%20that%20many%20brands%20would%20rather%20avoid.%20Weight-loss%20drugs%20are%20slimming%20down%20some%20proportion%20of%20the%20population%20and%20may%20be%20changing%20inventory%20mixes%20in%20turn.%20Many%20fashion%20retailers%20and%20companies%20have%20never%20been%20thrilled%20about%20catering%20to%20plus-size%20clients%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20American%20women%20are%20estimated%20to%20fall%20into%20that%20category%20%E2%80%94%20so%20they're%20happy%20to%20have%20a%20reason%20to%20turn%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20convinced%20at%20this%20point%20that%20they%20just%20want%20us%20running%20around%20naked%2C%26quot%3B%20Holliday%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20GLP-1%20explosion%2C%20brands%20that%20ventured%20into%20the%20plus-size%20market%20were%20already%20backing%20off.%20(I'll%20focus%20largely%20on%20women's%20fashion%20for%20this%20story%2C%20because%20that's%20where%20much%20of%20the%20spending%20and%20offerings%20are.)%20In%202021%2C%20Loft%20discontinued%20its%20plus-size%20options%20just%20three%20years%20after%20launching%20its%20first%20plus-size%20collection%2C%20citing%20%26quot%3Bongoing%20business%20challenges.%26quot%3B%20In%202022%2C%20Old%20Navy%20said%20it%20would%20pull%20some%20options%20from%20its%20stores%2C%20about%20a%20year%20after%20making%20a%20big%20deal%20about%20its%20efforts%20to%20place%20all%20sizes%20together%20on%20the%20sales%20floor%20instead%20of%20separating%20sections.%20The%20retailer%20still%20has%20plus-size%20clothing%2C%20it's%20just%20mostly%20online.%20In%20June%2C%20the%20plus-size%20retailer%20Torrid%20announced%20plans%20to%20close%20up%20to%20180%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Hope%20Krass%2C%20the%20host%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Flaurenhopekrass%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBelly%20Laughs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20body%20acceptance%20podcast%2C%20and%20a%20web%20series%20called%20%26quot%3BFat%20Fashion%2C%26quot%3B%20tells%20me%20the%20Loft%20pullback%20hurt%20a%20lot%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20the%20brand%20offers%20is%20business%20casual%20clothing.%20%26quot%3BYou'll%20hear%20a%20lot%20of%20plus-size%20shoppers%20complain%20about%2C%20'Well%2C%20we%20want%20sexy%20clothes%2C%20too.'%20And%20that%20is%20so%20true%2C%20but%20if%20you%20think%20about%20the%20country%2C%20we're%20business%20bitches%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20honestly%20really%20discouraging%20because%20we're%20seeing%20a%20loss%20of%20entire%20brands%20and%20companies%20go%20under.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnecdotally%2C%20plus-size%20shoppers%20and%20influencers%20say%20they've%20noticed%20a%20pullback%20in%20merchandise%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20retailers%2C%20including%20H%26amp%3BM.%20In%20addition%20to%20sharp-eyed%20shoppers%2C%20there's%20data%20to%20show%20that%20the%20extended-size%20clothing%20options%20are%20getting%20harder%20to%20find.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedited.com%2Freport%2Fsize-inclusivity-in-the-ozempic-era%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20retail%20intelligence%20firm%20Edited%20found%20that%20the%20clothing%20retailer%20Aritzia%20had%20cut%20the%20share%20of%202XL%20dresses%20among%20its%20new%20arrivals%20by%205%20percentage%20points%20from%202023%20while%20upping%20it%20in%20many%20smaller%20sizes.%20ASOS%20similarly%20reduced%20its%20plus-size%20assortment%20by%2015%25%20from%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20the%20report%20found%2C%20and%20Reformation%20reduced%20its%20extended%20sizing%20range%20by%2046%25.%20A%20separate%202024%20report%20from%20the%20merchandising%20and%20inventory%20consultancy%20Impact%20Analytics%20looked%20at%20Manhattan's%20Upper%20East%20Side%2C%20an%20affluent%20neighborhood%20where%20GLP-1s%20for%20weight%20loss%20were%20prominent%2C%20and%20found%20that%20sales%20in%20smaller%20sizes%20for%20women's%20button-down%20shirts%20increased%20by%2012%25%20for%20local%20fashion%20retailers%20from%202022%20to%202024%2C%20while%20sales%20of%20larger%20sizes%20fell%20by%20just%20slightly%20less.%20Impact%20Analytics%20found%20a%20similar%2C%20albeit%20less%20pronounced%2C%20trend%20for%20men.%20Executives%20at%20Lafayette%20148%2C%20Rent%20the%20Runway%2C%20and%20Amarra%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fretail%2Fozempic-clothing-sizes-weight-loss-80f9f83d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20that%20they'd%20spotted%20an%20uptick%20in%20customers%20switching%20to%20smaller%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20of%20Edited's%20report%20note%20that%20it's%20not%20clear%20whether%20Ozempic%20can%20be%20directly%20linked%20to%20increased%20demand%20for%20smaller%20sizes.%20Trendy%20weight-loss%20solutions%20are%20often%20coming%20and%20going%2C%20and%20only%20a%20tiny%20sliver%20of%20Americans%20are%20taking%20GLP-1s.%20But%20the%20fashion%20industry%20was%20already%20shifting%20away%20from%20plus%20size%20when%20the%20drugs%20hit%20the%20zeitgeist%2C%20and%20a%20scenario%20in%20which%20people%20lose%20weight%20and%20have%20to%20buy%20new%20clothes%20(and%20perhaps%20gain%20the%20weight%20back%20and%20have%20to%20buy%20more%20new%20clothes)%20is%20a%20great%20one%20for%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20breakthrough%20miracle%20drug%20for%20people%20who%20really%20need%20to%20lose%20weight%2C%20100%25.%20But%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20make%20everybody%20a%20Size%208%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Danielle%20Malconian%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20plus-size%20apparel%20brand%20Vikki%20Vi%20and%20the%20online%20retailer%20Plus%20by%20Design.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20easy%20thing%20for%20retailers%20to%20kind%20of%20jump%20out%20of%20the%20space%20because%20it%20is%20service-based.%20It%20is%20hard%3B%20it's%20not%20sexy%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20mentioned%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20country%20counts%20as%20plus%20size.%20For%20women%20in%20the%20US%2C%20that%20means%20those%20who%20wear%20a%20Size%2014%20and%20up.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fwhere-to-buy-plus-size-work-clothes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlus-size%20consumers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20spend%2C%20but%20that's%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20the%20most%20beautiful%20shoes%20and%20handbags%20of%20everybody%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20they%20get%20so%20frustrated%20that%20they%20can't%20find%20clothing%20to%20spend%20money%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Malconian%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fashion%20industry%20has%20long%20been%20hesitant%20to%20cater%20to%20plus-size%20customers.%20That's%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%20%E2%80%94%20some%20logistical%2C%20some%20cultural%2C%20some%20discriminatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesigning%20and%20manufacturing%20for%20plus-size%20customers%20can%20be%20more%20costly%20and%20intensive%20than%20for%20what%20are%20called%20%26quot%3Bstraight%20sizes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20industry%20term%20for%20the%20sizes%20you%20always%20find%20on%20the%20rack.%20Designers%20and%20brands%20often%20use%20one%20standard-size%20fit%20model%20and%20then%20scale%20up%20and%20down%20from%20there.%20But%20that%20gets%20harder%20to%20do%20in%20bigger%20sizes%20because%20of%20how%20differently%20people%20may%20carry%20their%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20making%20plus%20sizes%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20really%20concerned%20about%20fit%2C%20and%20when%20you're%20dealing%20with%20a%20plus-size%20customer%2C%20you're%20dealing%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20shapes%20of%20bodies%2C%26quot%3B%20Malconian%20says.%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20have%20not%20just%20one%20fit%20model%2C%20but%20maybe%20three%20or%20four%20fit%20models%20to%20really%20understand%20what's%20going%20to%20fit%2C%20or%20else%20you%20end%20up%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20returns%20and%20you%20go%20out%20of%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20material%20calculations%20make%20retailers%20less%20inclined%20to%20sell%20plus-size%20clothing%3A%20It%20requires%20more%20fabric%2C%20meaning%20it's%20more%20expensive%20to%20make.%20Retailers%20are%20hesitant%20to%20charge%20more%20for%20larger%20sizes%2C%20so%20they%20may%20order%20fewer%20units%20to%20put%20in%20their%20stores%2C%20if%20they%20carry%20them%20at%20all.%20E-commerce%20makes%20this%20all%20a%20little%20easier%20because%20it%20allows%20retailers%20to%20respond%20as%20orders%20come%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20online%2C%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20offer%20more%20inclusive%20sizes%20because%20we%20don't%20stock%20the%20inventory%20on%20our%20balance%20sheet%2C%20and%20we%20have%20the%20vendor%20cut%20it%20based%20on%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Shawn%20Grain%20Carter%2C%20a%20luxury%20branding%20and%20retail%20consultant%20who's%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20Fashion%20Institute%20of%20Technology.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20don't%20buy%20it%2C%20no%20harm%2C%20no%20foul%2C%20because%20you%20had%20that%20excess%20fabric%20sitting%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20downsizing%20of%20plus-size%20options%20is%20not%20just%20about%20logistical%20hurdles.%20Historically%2C%20the%20fashion%20industry%20has%20always%20prioritized%20being%20thin%2C%20and%20it%20caters%20to%20that%20clientele%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrass%20attributes%20the%20resistance%20to%20embracing%20plus-size%20fashion%20to%20plain%20%26quot%3Bfatphobia.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20get%20so%20annoyed%20when%20people%20are%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20our%20plus-size%20brands%20are%20going%20to%20go%20under%2C%20there's%20no%20more%20fat%20people%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20like%2C%20no%2C%20plus-size%20brands%20might%20go%20under%20due%20to%20fatphobia%2C%20not%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20fat%20people.%20We%20are%20here%2C%20and%20we%20should%20be%20here%20and%20should%20have%20the%20dignity%20of%20having%20access%20to%20fashion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECulturally%20and%20economically%2C%20plus-size%20people%20are%20often%20pushed%20to%20the%20side.%20Plus-size%20sections%20are%20often%20hidden%20away%20in%20stores.%20Brands%20that%20sell%20plus-size%20clothing%20often%20market%20them%20almost%20covertly.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20their%20Instagram%20posts%20and%20social%20media%20show%20straight-size%20models%2C%20even%20if%20they%20have%20plus-size%20merchandise.%20And%20the%20supposed%20plus-size%20models%20they%20do%20use%20are%20often%20still%20much%20thinner%20than%20their%20actual%20plus-size%20customers%2C%20who%20may%20not%20even%20really%20realize%20they're%20being%20targeted%20because%20models%20don't%20look%20like%20them%20in%20the%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20plus-size%20brands%20will%20default%20to%20showing%20Size%2014%20models%2C%20Size%2014%20people.%20To%20me%2C%20that's%20the%20midsize%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20Krass%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20shop%20straight%20sizes%2C%20so%20why%20are%20you%20catering%20to%20them%20for%20plus%20sizes%3F%20Get%20some%20thicker%20models%2C%20and%20we'll%20know%2C%20and%20then%20we'll%20shop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVogue%20Business'%20Autumn%2FWinter%202025%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voguebusiness.com%2Fstory%2Ffashion%2Fthe-vogue-business-autumn-winter-2025-size-inclusivity-report%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esize%20inclusivity%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20while%20%26quot%3Bcurvaceous%20silhouettes%26quot%3B%20were%20all%20over%20fashion%20show%20runways%2C%20curvy%20models%20were%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20danger%20of%20creating%20a%20false%20narrative%20yet%20again%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20only%20way%20one%20can%20look%20beautiful%20is%20to%20be%20skinny%2C%26quot%3B%20Carter%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2C%20of%20course%2C%20brands%20that%20have%20figured%20out%20that%20plus-size%20people%20have%20money%20and%20cater%20to%20them%20accordingly.%20Holliday%20points%20to%20Universal%20Standard%2C%20ASOS%2C%20and%20Eloquii%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-plus-size-clothing%23universal-standard-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrands%20getting%20it%20right%20on%20plus%20size%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20many%20more%20brands%20are%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20it%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Krass%20points%20out%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-shopping-secondhand-tariffs-recession-goodwill-ebay-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresale%20and%20thrifting%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20especially%20popular%20among%20plus-size%20shoppers%2C%20especially%20as%20brands%20pull%20back%20on%20new%20merchandise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOzempic%20and%20other%20GLP-1s%20may%20change%20the%20lay%20of%20the%20land%20in%20plus-size%20fashion%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20make%20the%20need%20for%20such%20options%20obsolete.%20These%20medications%20are%20not%20widely%20available%20and%20accessible.%20They're%20costly%20and%20often%20not%20covered%20by%20insurance.%20And%20they're%20not%20for%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20they%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20side%20effects%2C%20and%20one%20study%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamanetworkopen%2Ffullarticle%2F2819256%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20half%20of%20the%20people%20who%20take%20them%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20weight%20loss%20quit%20within%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20everybody%20suddenly%20being%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20everybody%20can%20be%20skinny%20now.'%20If%20they%20could%20all%20be%20skinny%2C%20why%20are%20there%20still%20fat%20people%3F%26quot%3B%20Holliday%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20GLP-1s%20won't%20get%20rid%20of%20obesity%2C%20they%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20brands%20and%20retailers%20to%20ignore%20heavier%20people.%20The%20fashion%20industry%20wants%20to%20be%20aspirational%2C%20and%20American%20culture%20aspires%20to%20skinny%2C%20even%20if%20that's%20not%20realistic%20or%20even%20savvy%20business-wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%2C%20when%20we%20go%20in%20stores%2C%20is%20our%20stuff%20all%20the%20way%20in%20the%20back%2C%20hidden%20in%20a%20corner%3F%26quot%3B%20Holliday%20says.%20%26quot%3BIs%20that%20Mounjaro's%20fault%3F%20No.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplus-size-clothing-ozempic-glp-1-weight-loss-drugs-shopping-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751963581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686577fef748d8c055f4d8ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplus-size-clothing-ozempic-glp-1-weight-loss-drugs-shopping-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rise%20