eautiful%26quot%3B%20tax%20and%20spending%20bill%20into%20law%20on%20July%204.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bill%20eliminates%20the%20Grad%20PLUS%20student-loan%20program%20and%20caps%20borrowing%20for%20graduates%20and%20professional%20students.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20caps%20could%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20some%20students%20to%20get%20their%20advanced%20degrees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20soon%20be%20harder%20to%20attend%20medical%20or%20law%20school%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edue%20to%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-passes-big-beautiful-bill-trump-signing-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebig%20spending%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20signed%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-big-beautiful-bill-impacts-wallet-taxes-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bbig%20beautiful%26quot%3B%20tax%20and%20spending%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20law%20on%20July%204%2C%20codifying%20a%20slew%20of%20changes%20to%20the%20tax%20system%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20education.%20The%20law%20includes%20a%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-major-repayment-overhaul-big-beautiful-bill-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoverhaul%20to%20the%20country's%20education%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20to%20the%20way%20students%20take%20out%20and%20pay%20off%20their%20student%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20specific%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-trump-spending-bill-changes-parent-plus-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudent-loan%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20bill%20places%20new%20caps%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20loans%20students%20can%20borrow%20for%20graduate%20school%2C%20including%20medical%20and%20law%20school.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20bill%20eliminates%20the%20Grad%20PLUS%20loan%20program%2C%20which%20allowed%20graduate%20and%20professional%20students%20to%20borrow%20up%20to%20the%20full%20cost%20of%20attendance%20for%20their%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20caps%20borrowing%20for%20graduate%20students%20at%20%2420%2C500%20a%20year%20and%20%24100%2C000%20over%20a%20lifetime%20and%20for%20professional%20students%2C%20like%20those%20in%20medical%20or%20law%20school%2C%20at%20%2450%2C000%20a%20year%20and%20%24200%2C000%20over%20a%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20Trump's%20spending%20bill%20affecting%20your%20decision%20to%20pursue%20an%20advanced%20degree%2C%20like%20medical%20or%20law%3F%20Share%20your%20story%20with%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20caps%20mean%20many%20students%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20borrow%20enough%20to%20cover%20the%20full%20price%20of%20graduate%20or%20professional%20school.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Association%20of%20American%20Medical%20Colleges%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstore.aamc.org%2Fdownloadable%2Fdownload%2Fsample%2Fsample_id%2F633%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20median%20cost%20for%20four%20years%20of%20public%20medical%20school%20was%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%24286%2C454%20for%20the%20class%20of%202024%2C%20with%20that%20amount%20rising%20to%20just%20over%20%24390%2C000%20at%20a%20private%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20total%20cost%20of%20law%20school%20in%20the%20latest%20school%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feducationdata.org%2Faverage-cost-of-law-school%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Education%20Data%20Initiative%2C%20was%20just%20over%20%24217%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEliminating%20or%20restricting%20these%20critical%20programs%20would%20undermine%20the%20future%20physician%20workforce%20and%20ultimately%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20patients%20in%20communities%20nationwide%20to%20get%20the%20care%20they%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20AAMC's%20president%20and%20CEO%2C%20David%20Skorton%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aamc.org%2Fnews%2Fproposed-changes-federal-student-loans-could-worsen-doctor-shortage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESara%20Partridge%2C%20associate%20director%20for%20higher%20education%20policy%20at%20the%20left-leaning%20think%20tank%20Center%20for%20American%20Progress%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20expects%20these%20new%20caps%20to%20worsen%20doctor%20shortages%20and%20%26quot%3Bshut%20off%20pathways%20to%20these%20important%20jobs%20for%20students%20from%20low%20income%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Health%20Resources%20and%20Services%20Administration%20%E2%80%94%20a%20federal%20agency%20that%20ensures%20healthcare%20access%20%E2%80%94%20said%20in%20a%202024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbhw.hrsa.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fbureau-health-workforce%2Fstate-of-the-health-workforce-report-2024.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2075%20million%20people%20currently%20live%20in%20a%20primary%20care%20health%20shortage%20area%2C%20and%20it%20projects%20a%20shortage%20of%20187%2C130%20full-time%20physicians%20in%202037.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20students%20might%20also%20turn%20toward%20private%20student%20loans%20with%20higher%20interest%20rates%2C%20Partridge%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrivate%20student%20loans%20often%20require%20a%20cosigner%2C%20so%20some%20students%20may%20not%20qualify%2C%20and%20they%20may%20have%20no%20options%20to%20fully%20finance%20and%20attend%20graduate%20school.%20So%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20for%20some%20students%2C%20this%20will%20be%20a%20barrier%20to%20accessing%20graduate%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20Partridge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20parent%20PLUS%20program%2C%20which%20previously%20allowed%20parents%20to%20borrower%20up%20to%20the%20full%20cost%20of%20attendance%2C%20still%20exists%2C%20but%20the%20bill%20places%20a%20%2465%2C000%20lifetime%20cap%20on%20parents%20borrowing%20for%20their%20kids'%20educations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20borrowing%20caps%2C%20the%20spending%20bill%20also%20instituted%20significant%20changes%20to%20student-loan%20repayment.%20It%20eliminated%20existing%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%20and%20replaced%20them%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgop-plan-student-loan-borrowers-longer-repayment-less-debt-cancellation-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etwo%20new%20options%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20first%20option%20is%20a%20standard%20repayment%20plan%20with%20a%20payment%20period%20ranging%20from%2010%20to%2025%20years%2C%20based%20on%20the%20borrower's%20original%20balance.%20The%20second%20option%20is%20a%20new%20plan%20called%20the%20Repayment%20Assistance%20Plan%2C%20which%20sets%20borrowers'%20payments%20at%201%25%20to%2010%25%20of%20their%20income%2C%20and%20any%20remaining%20balance%20is%20forgiven%20after%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20less%20generous%20than%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-cheaper-payments-debt-cancellation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESAVE%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20bill%20eliminated.%20The%20SAVE%20plan%20would%20have%20reduced%20payments%20on%20undergraduate%20loans%20from%2010%25%20to%205%25%20of%20a%20borrower's%20discretionary%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinda%20McMahon%2C%20Trump's%20education%20secretary%2C%20lauded%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20bill%20in%20a%20July%203%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FEDSecMcMahon%2Fstatus%2F1940842608210989328%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%2C%20saying%20it%20%26quot%3Bsi