company%20APR%20Corp.%2C%20became%20the%20country's%20newest%20billionaire.%20With%20a%2031%25%20stake%20in%20the%20company%2C%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index%20on%20Monday%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-07-07%2Fkardashian-endorsed-k-beauty-s-medicube-makes-korean-founder-a-billionaire%3Fsrnd%3Dhomepage-americas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elisted%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Kim's%20net%20worth%20as%20%241.3%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAPR%20Corp.%20has%20numerous%20South%20Korean%20brands%20under%20its%20umbrella%2C%20including%20beauty%20brands%20Aprilskin%20and%20Forment%2C%20and%20supplements%20brand%20Glam.D%20Bio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20is%20a%20young%20leader%20with%20a%20strong%20social%20media%20presence.%20The%20CEO%20has%20more%20than%2024%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram%2C%20where%20he%20posts%20content%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20star%20of%20APR%20Corp.'s%20brand%20portfolio%20is%20Medicube%2C%20a%20beauty%20tech%20company%20whose%20skincare%20devices%20have%20been%20touted%20by%20celebrities%20like%20Kylie%20Jenner%20and%20Hailey%20Bieber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20April%20TikTok%20video%2C%20Jenner%20said%20she%20stopped%20by%20Medicube's%20pop-up%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20picked%20up%20the%20brand's%20Booster%20Pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMedicube's%20website%20says%20the%20Booster%20Pro%2C%20a%20slender%20%24240%20cylindrical%20device%2C%20enhances%20%26quot%3Babsorption%2C%20radiance%2C%20elasticity%2C%26quot%3B%20helps%20with%20pores%2C%20and%20gives%20skin%20the%20%26quot%3Bglass%20glow%26quot%3B%20that%20Korean%20beauty%20is%20synonymous%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenner%20was%20seen%20using%20it%20in%20her%20skincare%20routine%20as%20she%20applied%20products%20to%20her%20face.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20website%2C%20APR%20Corp%2C%20then%20Aprilskin%20Corporation%2C%20was%20founded%20in%202014.%20It%20launched%20Medicube%20in%202016%2C%20which%20expanded%20globally%20in%20the%20following%20years.%20Medicube%20launched%20the%20Booster%20Pro%20in%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim's%20company%20went%20public%20in%20February%202024%20and%20now%20has%20a%20market%20capitalization%20of%20about%20%244.2%20billion.%20Its%20stock%20was%20trading%20at%20158%2C300%20Korean%20won%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20or%20about%20%24116%2C%20up%20more%20than%2075%25%20since%20its%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim's%20entry%20into%20the%20billionaires%20club%20comes%20as%20Korean%20beauty%20is%20gaining%20popularity%2C%20with%20brands%20like%20Beauty%20of%20Joseon%2C%20Laneige%2C%20and%20Dr.%20Jart%2B%20going%20viral%20on%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EK%20Beauty's%20promise%20of%20delivering%20glass%20skin%20goes%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bglazed%20skin%26quot%3B%20trend%20that%20Hailey%20Bieber%2C%20founder%20of%20skincare%20brand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frhode-elf-beauty-made-mark-on-beauty-world-3-years-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERhode%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20coined.%20Bieber%2C%20too%2C%20made%20a%20video%20in%20July%202023%20using%20Medicube's%20Booster-H%2C%20an%20older%20version%20of%20the%20Booster%20Pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20APR%20Corp.%20and%20Jenner%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-kim-byung-hoon-beauty-billionaire-kylie-jenner-fan-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751959849000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686c940af748d8c055f51e28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-kim-byung-hoon-beauty-billionaire-kylie-jenner-fan-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20a%2031%25%20stake%20in%20APR%20Corp.%2C%20CEO%20and%20beauty%20mogul%20Kim%20Byung-Hoon%20now%20has%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%241.3%20billi