%20it%20to%20more%20easily%20communicate%2C%20operate%20computers%2C%20or%20play%20video%20games.%20Musk%20has%20said%20that%20the%20ability%20for%20humans%20to%20integrate%20directly%20with%20machines%20can%20help%20ensure%20human%20control%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20in%20a%202021%20podcast%20appearance%20that%20he%20created%20Neuralink%20%26quot%3Bspecifically%20to%20address%20the%20AI%20symbiosis%20problem%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20an%20existential%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2234841ea0-d024-4b83-b9bb-c8aea55915c3%5C%22%3EMusk's%20political%20problem-solving%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20speaking%20at%20a%20town%20hall%20in%20Lancaster%2C%20Pennsylvania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686b2fae3d5881a51c1cc1b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BBy%20a%20factor%20of%202%20to%201%2C%20you%20want%20a%20new%20political%20party%20and%20you%20shall%20have%20it!%26quot%3B%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20when%20announcing%20the%20formation%20of%20his%20new%20political%20party%20after%20conducting%20a%20poll%20on%20X.%3Cp%3ESamuel%20Corum%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20apply%20the%20same%20strategy%20to%20solving%20massive%20political%20challenges%2C%20said%20Sonnenfeld%2C%20the%20Yale%20professor%2C%20who's%20also%20the%20founder%20of%20Yale's%20Chief%20Executive%20Leadership%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20great%20as%20a%20technology%20creator%20and%20entrepreneur%2C%20but%20not%20great%20in%20turnarounds%20and%20has%20been%20quite%20ham-handed%20in%20government%2C%20if%20not%20brutally%20offensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Sonnenfeld%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20efforts%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%2C%20Musk%20set%20out%20to%20cut%20what%20he%20described%20as%20fraudulent%20or%20exc