47%2C500%20tax%20credit%20established%20under%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20EV%20initiative%20will%20expire%20on%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20in%20the%20market%20for%20an%20EV%20and%20you're%20ready%20to%20commit%20to%20a%20new%20car%2C%20you%20should%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Joseph%20Yoon%2C%20consumer%20insights%20analyst%20at%20car%20shopping%20website%20Edmunds%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERevised%20rules%20for%20the%20%247%2C500%20federal%20tax%20credit%20went%20into%20effect%20last%20year%20and%20limited%20the%20number%20of%20EVs%20that%20qualified%20for%20the%20credit.%20However%2C%2020%20electric%20and%20hybrid%20vehicles%2C%20including%20all%20of%20Tesla's%20models%20and%20the%20Ford%20F150%20Lightning%2C%20still%20qualify%20for%20the%20discount%20(you%20can%20check%20out%20the%20full%20list%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-the-evs-set-to-lose-the-federal-tax-credit-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20auto%20manufacturers%2C%20like%20Slate%20Auto%2C%20have%20already%20started%20to%20adjust%20their%20listings.%20The%20Jeff%20Bezos-backed%20EV%20startup%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslate-auto-ditches-under-20-000-price-tag-for-pickup-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erecently%20removed%20the%20%26quot%3Bunder%20%2420%2C000%26quot%3B%20expected%20price%20tag%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20upcoming%20EV%20pickup%20truck%2C%20which%20the%20company%20previously%20expected%20to%20qualify%20for%20federal%20tax%20incentives.%20Now%20it%20says%20it's%20expected%20to%20cost%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bmid-twenties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20EV%20tax%20credit%20has%20two%20parts.%20Consumers%20can%20qualify%20for%20a%20%243%2C750%20credit%20if%20the%20vehicle%20meets%20either%20the%20critical%20minerals%20or%20battery%20component%20requirements.%20If%20it%20satisfies%20both%20criteria%2C%20consumers%20can%20get%20the%20full%20%247%2C500%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20qualify%20for%20the%20%247%2C500%20incentive%2C%20several%20additional%20criteria%20must%20be%20met%3A%20the%20vehicle%20must%20have%20a%20battery%20capacity%20of%20at%20least%207%20kilowatt-hours%2C%20a%20gross%20vehicle%20weight%20rating%20under%2014%2C000%20pounds%2C%20and%20final%20assembly%20must%20take%20place%20in%20North%20America.%20Additionally%2C%20at%20least%2050%25%20of%20the%20battery's%20minerals%20and%20components%20must%20be%20sourced%20from%20the%20US%20or%20a%20country%20with%20a%20US%20free-trade%20agreement.%20There's%20also%20a%20suggested%20price%20cap%20for%20the%20incentive%20to%20apply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsed%20EVS%20also%20have%20a%20clean%20vehicle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fcredits-deductions%2Fused-clean-vehicle-credit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etax%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allows%20certain%20buyers%20in%20an%20income%20bracket%20to%20be%20eligible%20for%20up%20to%20%244%2C000%20for%20an%20EV%20with%20a%20sale%20price%20of%20%2425%2C000%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Moody%2C%20lead%20senior%20editor%20for%20Autotrader%20and%20Kelley%20Blue%20Book%2C%20said%20that%20buyers%20in%20search%20of%20a%20used%20EV%20should%20also%20strive%20to%20make%20a%20purchase%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Long-term%2C%20though%2C%20it%20won't%20make%20too%20much%20of%20a%20difference%20because%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-used-car-sales-increase-average-sale-price-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEVs%20%26quot%3Bdepreciate%20very%20rapidly%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20Moody%20said.%20The%20average%201%20to%205-year-old%20used%20EV%20price%20is%20around%20%2431%2C110%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iseecars.com%2Fused-car-prices-study%23v%3D202505%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20data%20from%20iSeeCars.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20without%20the%20incentive%2C%20they're%20still%20going%20to%20end%20up%20being%20a%20great%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20Moody%20said%20about%20used%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20EVs%20are%20another%20story%20%E2%80%94%20often%20commanding%20higher%20price%20tags%20than%20their%20gas-powered%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoon%20said%20the%20average%20sticker%20price%20of%20a%20new%20EV%20is%20%2463%2C026%2C%20and%20the%20average%20manufacturer's%20suggested%20retail%20price%20for%20a%20gas%20car%20is%20%2450%2C273.%20While%20not%20having%20the%20%247%2C500%20rebate%20will%20have%20an%20impact%2C%20some%20manufacturers%20may%20add%20their%20own%20discounts%20and%20incentives%20to%20help%20move%20inventory%2C%20Yoon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20happen%20to%20be%20on%20the%20fence%20about%20getting%20an%20EV%20and%20you're%20not%20in%20the%20place%20for%20a%20big-ticket%20purchase%2C%20there%20may%20be%20some%20benefit%20to%20waiting.%20With%20the%20incentives%20increasing%20competition%20in%20the%20market%2C%20some%20auto%20manufacturers%20may%20up%20their%20game%20to%20convince%20buyers%20to%20convert%2C%20Moody%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20end%20up%20making%20electric%20cars%20better%20overall%20because%20they'll%20have%20to%20now%20compete%20on%20an%20even%20playing%20field%20with%20cars%20that%20are%20powered%20by%20all%20different%20types%20of%20fuels%2C%20whether%20it's%20hydrogen%2C%20electric%2C%20or%20just%20gas%2C%26quot%3B%20Moody%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20wouldn't%20happen%20overnight%20or%20in%20the%20near-term%20future%2C%20given%20that%20manufacturers%20will%20have%20to%20work%20on%20outsourcing%2C%20tariffs%2C%20and%20price%20adjustments.%20However%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20long-term%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20were%20already%20planning%20on%20buying%20a%20new%20EV%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20and%20can%20afford%20it%20%E2%80%94%20you%20might%20as%20well%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20federal%20incentive%20while%20you%20still%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgood-time-buy-electric-car-before-ev-tax-credit-expires-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751922976000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6866ea5085e81483682d643c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgood-time-buy-electric-car-before-ev-tax-credit-expires-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill%20is%20set%20to%20end%20the%20Biden-era%20%247%2C500%20tax%20credit%20for%20new%20EVs%2C%20and%20up%20to%20%244%2C000%20credit%20for%20used%20ones%2C%20on%20September%2030.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A66%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgood-time-buy-electric-car-before-ev-tax-credit-expires-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20my%204-year-old%20named%20her%20imaginary%20friend%20'Instagram%2C'%20I%20was%20mortified.%20It%20was%20a%20sign%20I%20needed%20to%20adjust%20my%20own%20screen%20time.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20poses%20while%20swimming%20in%20the%20ocean%20with%20two%20kids.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685e99eaf748d8c055f47ebe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20on%20vacation%20my%20daughter%20started%20talking%20about%20an%20imaginary%20friend.%20The%20name%20she%20chose%20shocked%20me.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alexandra%20Meyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20enjoying%20a%20family%20vacation%20when%20my%20daughter%20started%20playing%20with%20some%20imaginary%20friends.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20horrified%20to%