ed-and-hundreds-injured-as-135mph-winds-hit-taiwan-13393561%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20500%20injured%20as%20Typhoon%20Danas%20brought%20record%20winds%20of%20135mph%20to%20Taiwan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftyphoon-danas-two-people-killed-and-hundreds-injured-as-135mph-winds-hit-taiwan-13393561%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Andhra-Based%20Chocolate%20Brand%20Empowered%20300%2B%20Farmers%20%26amp%3B%20Earned%20Rs%208.7%20Cr%20in%20Year%20One%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBehind%20every%20chocolate%20bar%20lies%20the%20story%20of%20a%20farmer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20%3Cem%3EManam%20Chocolate%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20story%20begins%20in%20the%20cocoa%20farms%20of%20West%20Godavari%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Belgian%20nor%20Swiss%2C%20this%20chocolate%20is%20proudly%20and%20entirely%20Indian.%20With%20over%20300%20products%20across%2050%20categories%2C%20Manam%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262803%2Fmumbai-woman-entrepreneur-healthy-snacks-oats-flax-seeds-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChocolate%20is%20redefining%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20perception%20of%20Indian-origin%20cocoa%20on%20the%20world%20stage.%20And%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20it%20is%20a%20deep%20commitment%20to%20craft%2C%20community%2C%20and%20cocoa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2015%2C%202023%2C%20Manam%20Chocolate%20launched%20its%20first%20collection%20in%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20Banjara%20Hills%20%E2%80%94%20a%20proud%20tribute%20to%20the%20farmers%20who%20made%20it%20all%20possible.%20Among%20its%20most%20celebrated%20offerings%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3EManam%20Signature%20Tablet%3C%2Fem%3E%20collection%2C%20featuring%2043%20unique%20bars.%20Two%20of%20these%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EFarm%20Tablet%20No.1%3C%2Fem%3E%20and