%3Cp%3EThey%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20a%20fancy%20van%2C%20corporate%20sponsors%2C%20or%20expensive%20equipment.%20Just%20a%20cycle.%20A%20dog.%20A%20will.%20And%20a%20lot%20of%20heart.%20Sonu%20puts%20it%20best%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20humans%20are%20much%20more%20terrifying%20than%20any%20stray%20dog.%20Dogs%20just%20want%20love.%20Charlie%20never%20needed%20disciplining%E2%80%94she%20just%20needed%20someone%20to%20stay.%20And%20I%20stayed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20gear%20up%20for%20their%20next%20ride%20through%20the%20hills%20and%20valleys%20of%20the%20Northeast%2C%20Sonu%20and%20Charlie%20continue%20pedalling%20not%20just%20across%20India%2C%20but%20straight%20into%20people%E2%80%99s%20hearts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20help%20Sonu%20achieve%20his%20dream%20of%20opening%20his%20animal%20shelter%20in%20Bihar%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%2072004%2022273.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751639400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-04T185120.827-1751635404.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D462784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Sonu%20Raj%20met%20an%20injured%20stray%20puppy%20on%20the%20highway%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20she%20would%20change%20his%20life%20forever.%20Today%2C%20he%20and%20Charlie%20have%20cycled%20across%2015%20states%E2%80%94proving%20that%20love%2C%20grit%2C%20and%20compassion%20can%20take%20you%20anywhere.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F462784%2Fsonu-raj-charlie-cycle-journey-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2268%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Snow%20Leopards%20Are%20in%20Ladakh%20And%20Locals%20Helped%20Make%20It%20Happen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C