gh%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20low-density%20zones.%20These%20traps%20captured%20over%2026%2C000%20images.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20software%20called%20CaTRAT%2C%20trained%20specifically%20to%20recognise%20Himalayan%20wildlife%2C%20scientists%20identified%20individual%20snow%20leopards%20by%20the%20unique%20patterns%20on%20their%20foreheads%2C%20more%20reliable%20than%20side%20markings%2C%20which%20can%20be%20distorted%20by%20wind-ruffled%20fur.%20From%20126%20identified%20individuals%2C%20the%20team%20used%20spatial%20capture-recapture%20models%20to%20estimate%20a%20total%20population%20of%20477%20snow%20leopards%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ladakh%20is%20home%20to%20an%20estimated%20477%20snow%20leopards%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Bubo%20Birding%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Works