0family%20can%20monopolise%20the%20tourists.%20Because%20if%20that%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20create%20disharmony%20in%20the%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESafeguarding%20livestock%20and%20landscapes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conservancy%20also%20supports%20the%20construction%20of%20predator-proof%20livestock%20enclosures%20using%20low-cost%20and%20locally%20sourced%20materials.%20%E2%80%9CVillagers%20provide%20the%20labour%20while%20SLC-IT%20provides%20wire%20mesh%2C%20doorframes%2C%20beams%2C%20and%20wooden%20poles%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Namgail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snow%20leopard%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20maintaining%20ecological%20balance.%20It%20preys%20on%20herbivores%20such%20as%20the%20Himalayan%20blue%20sheep%20and%20Asiatic%20ibex%2C%20keeping%20their%20populations%20in%20check%20and%20preventing%20overgrazing.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20herbivores%20feed%20on%20alpine%20pastures%20that%20grow%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F321695%2Faamir-khanyari-turned-ancestral-land-into-traditional-kashmir-homestay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslopes%20of%20the%20mountain%20ranges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20controlling%20the%20population%20of%20these%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20the%20snow%20leopard%20gives%20the%20grasses%20and%20plants%20a%20chance%20to%20regenerate%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Namgail%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20snow%20leopard%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20maintaining%20ecological%20balance%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wild%20Images%5C%22%20srcset%3